args.new_str:
def get_filtered_matrix(group_option, prompt_variation, model_id, excluded_ids):
    group_list = group_mappings[group_option]
    full_group_list = ['a person'] + group_list
    matrix = np.zeros((len(full_group_list), len(full_group_list)))
    
    for i, persona in enumerate(full_group_list):
        for j, experiencer in enumerate(full_group_list):
            intensity_list, _ = get_intensity_list(group_option, prompt_variation, model_id, persona, experiencer)
            filtered_intensity_list = [intensity for idx, intensity in enumerate(intensity_list) if idx not in excluded_ids]
            if filtered_intensity_list:
                matrix[i][j] = np.mean(filtered_intensity_list)
    
    mean = np.mean(matrix)
    std = np.std(matrix)
    standardized_matrix = (matrix - mean) / std
    
    return standardized_matrix
